<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆一路走进了黑暗森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>森林里可怕极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皇宫在哪里呢？”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆遇到了一个小贩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道皇宫在哪里吗？”汤姆问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“知道啊。”小贩说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它一直就在那里，你真笨！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个人真没礼貌。”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆又走了一会儿, 但他还是没看到皇宫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出了地图。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一阵冷风刮过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢！”汤姆害怕得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在行李里找了找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>找出了他的手套，但他的毛皮帽子去哪里了?</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要变出一顶新帽子来！”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用魔杖指着自己的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛皮帽子！”他说。噗！ 噗！ 噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他头顶上有个温暖而毛茸茸的东西啦！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我成功了!”汤姆自豪地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这个时候，冷风又刮了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地图从汤姆手上飞走了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地图飞进了树林里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老师告诉过我不要离开小路。”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我需要那张地图啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆紧张地离开了小路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在森林里越走越深。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，汤姆停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他感觉到头上有什么东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的毛皮帽子在动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>